dataIdInfo.idAbs: The dataset represents the Grama Niladhari Divisions of Sri Lanka. DISCLAIMER: Admin4 Tamil names are not available. The English and Sinhalese names of some units are unknown.

Consts.useLimit: See the COD/FOD Registry Terms of Use. This does not replace any terms of use information provided with the dataset.

dataIdInfo.idPurp: Administrative Level 4 Boundaries of Sri Lanka

dataLineage.statement:
Layer was downloaded by ITOS from HDX. It was then analyzed by ITOS for errors. Those errors were corrected and then the layer was sent back to UNOCHA as a feature class within a file geodatabase.
The following errors were found and fixed by ITOS: 1. Admin3 names converted to Proper Case from ALL CAPS. 2. Roman numerals in names converted to Proper Case. 3. Fixed spacing errors in Admin3 name "Galle4Gravets". 4. Inserted spaces before parenthetical names in 10 Admin3 names. 5. Fixed gaps in Admin4 units "Kowtharimunai", "Umaiyalpuram", "Nallur, "Iranaithivu" and "Urithirapuram North". 6. Fixed multipart sliver errors in units "Panape" and "Neelapola". 7. Admin3 units “Walapane” and “Nildandahinna” both had Sinhalese name "වලපනේ". Bangkok regional office has sent this correction/update: "NILDANDAHINNA ,නිල්දණ්ඩාහින්න, நீல்தண்டாஹின்ன". 8. Fixed a gap between units "Periyaneelavanai 01A" and "Periyaneelavanai 01B".
The following errors were found by ITOS but are not addressed in this version: 1. 21 Admin4 units have duplicated names within the same Admin3. Their p-codes are unique. An export of these Admin4 units named "Same_Name_Same_Admin3" can be found in the Supporting_Info.gdb 2. 171 Admin4 names do not have a 1 to 1 relationship between English and Sinhala names. An export of these names called "Admin4_EN_SI_Conflicts" is located in Supporting_Info.gdb 3. Some names include parentheses. These may indicate AltNames that should be separated and placed in an AltName field. 4.The name of some units is unknown 5. Admin4 unit "Alim Nagar" has two multipart polygons that need inspection.
